title: Conair Straight Waves 3-in-1 Specialty Styler
description: Get maximum efficiency from your hairstyling tools with this five-in-one style set from Conair. With its five interchangeable heads, the iron lets you curl, spiral, wave, crimp, and straighten your hair. The kit includes a 1/2-inch spiral head and a 3/4-inch curling iron. The round brush attachment is also 3/4 inches. The double-sided crimping and straightening plates are especially clever--they reverse from one to the other to suit your look. All the attachments feature convenient stay-cool tips, while a locking collar on the base keeps them secure during use. The unit also features a simple on/off switch, a ready indicator button, a built-in resting stand on the curl and spiral attachments, and a 6-foot power cord.--Emily Bedard
